# 🚀 Docker Flask CI/CD Application

Production-style Dockerized Flask application with Jenkins CI/CD and Amazon ECR integration.

---

# 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates a real-world DevOps workflow using:

- Docker
- Docker Compose
- Jenkins Pipeline
- Amazon ECR
- Python Flask Application
- GitHub Integration

The goal of this repository is to understand containerization, image lifecycle management, CI/CD automation, and cloud-native deployment workflows.

---

# 🧠 Architecture

```text
Developer
    ↓
GitHub Repository
    ↓
Jenkins Pipeline
    ↓
Docker Build
    ↓
Amazon ECR
    ↓
Container Deployment
```

---

# ⚙️ Technologies Used

| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Docker | Containerization |
| Jenkins | CI/CD Automation |
| Flask | Python Web Application |
| Amazon ECR | Container Registry |
| GitHub | Source Code Management |
| Docker Compose | Multi-container orchestration |

