# 📌 Final Note

This repository is focused on learning production-style DevOps workflows using Docker, Jenkins, and AWS.

The objective is not only to run containers locally but also to understand:

- CI/CD automation
- image versioning
- container lifecycle
- deployment workflows
- registry management
- cloud-native concepts

This project will continue evolving toward ECS, EKS, and Kubernetes-based deployments.